    <h2 class="section"> URL References</h2> <!-- begin section URL References-->

      <h3 class="drop-down-header" onclick="toggleText('DescendingTip')">How to display grouped records in descending order</h3>
        <p id="DescendingTip" class="hidden-text">The first parameter will sort in Ascending order whilst the latter in Descending order.<br><br>
        &sysparm_group_sort=COUNT<br>
        &sysparm_group_sort=COUNTDESC<br><br>
        If the above doesn't work, try one of these 2 parameters<br><br>
        %26sysparm_group_sort%3DCOUNTDESC<br>
        %26sysparm_group_sort%3DCOUNT<br>
        </p>

    <!-- end section URL References-->

